1. Introduction
--------------------------------------------------------------

A Java program is written using a fixed structure.

Every Java program contains different parts such as:

• Package (Optional)
• Import Statement (Optional)
• Class Declaration
• Main Method
• Statements
• Comments

Understanding the structure of a Java program is very
