→ Executes code multiple times.

Q2. Types of loops?
→ for, while, do-while

Q3. Difference between while and do-while?
→ do-while executes at least once.

Q4. When to use for loop?
→ When iterations are known.

Q5. What is nested loop?
→ Loop inside another loop.

