2. Write into a file
3. Read a file
4. Delete a file
5. Modify a file

==============================================================
5. FILE CLASS
==============================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------
Definition:
--------------------------------------------------------------

File class is used to create and manage files and directories.

==============================================================
6. CREATE FILE EXAMPLE
==============================================================
```java id="f1"
import java.io.File;
import java.io.IOException;

public class Demo {

